---
import SectionHeader from "../SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section class="contact-faq">

  <div class="container">

    <SectionHeader
      
      title="Frequently Asked Questions"
      description="Quick answers to common questions from architects, designers, distributors, and project buyers."
    />

    <div class="faq-list">

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>What is your MOQ?</h3>

        <p>
          MOQ can start from a single piece depending on the product.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>Can you customize dimensions?</h3>

        <p>
          Yes. Most products can be manufactured to custom sizes.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>Do you ship worldwide?</h3>

        <p>
          Yes. We regularly export to Europe, North America, Australia and other regions.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>How long is production?</h3>

        <p>
          Lead time depends on product complexity and order quantity.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>